data.description: Move in ready one level living with two car garage with storage. Open floor plan, large kitchen with tons of granite counter space, tile backsplash and soft close cabinets, stainless appliances. Screened in and open grilling deck, hot tub. Fenced in backyard with Gazebo and storage building. The master bedroom features two oversized closets and en suite bathroom complete with granite counter top. Two additional bedrooms, full bath and laundry room. New flooring in the kitchen and living room/dining room area. New hot water heater.
